    "body": "This will add the flag -fiopenmp when building codes with oneapi that have the openmp variant. \r\n\r\nThere is an additional flag -fopenmp-target=spir64 which is needed to build device code (only builds host code without this) and I propose this as a variant +spir to be added to packages (e.g. kokkos: https://github.com/spack/spack/pull/23770) as needed. ",
